{"tid":2329634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網購網着屎 有冇人係呢間買過野？","createTime":"2020-12-17T10:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T11:26:52.000Z","uid":255944,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93b37a4a8e439f59a1f08bf51716909aabb7f241","tid":2329634,"uid":255944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黑店Yayen.mart </span></span></strong><br />\n(以我所知佢仲有個Facebook page)<br />\n<br />\nSor for長文<br />\n<br />\n事源係咁, 5/9係呢間鋪同朋友夾訂左2盒心太軟預伴粉, 當時話11月中會到貨, 而我ok左當晚都payme左俾店主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後尾等等下都唔記得左, 直至23/11醒起夜晚就dm店主, 店主隔日朝早cap左個商家對話既whatsapp圖俾我, 內容意思大約係指供應商未返貨遲左 所以未有貨 (dm張圖睇一次, 不過當時不誤有咋所以冇cap底), 話有貨會再通知我, 咁我諗住小店做生意都唔易所以冇太計較 直接話ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到9/12, 兩個幾星期後店主都冇再follow up我, 我再搵佢, 呢到就開始黎. 分別係9/12, 12/12, 16/12搵過店主, 完全不讀不回, 但當中既日子係keep住出post去賣商品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到今日(17/12)再dm留過, 電話打過都冇人應, 都預左冇左錢同貨, 當今次係唔好彩俾黑店呃左, 但覺得唔應該就咁不了了之等間店再呃下個客, 最後就係post留言提醒下個人唔好呢間野呃錢冇貨收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個店主就好快出現左 (亦即係話佢一直知我dm過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) , 話今個星期再覆我,叫我比埋順豐編號 名同電話,一句sorry/原因都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗住唔想嘈落去退錢算, 點知店主話因為而家有貨寄 所以唔會退錢. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />首先點知店主又拖我幾耐, 再黎今次係買食材, 要放落口, 而家搞到咁不愉快, 要死追難追, 由話未有貨到廠商而家突然有貨, 完全唔知店主俾咩貨或者邊到黎, 我點敢收！無辦法我下我話只好報警, 再後來同朋友傾完, 佢話當收貨買個教訓算, 無謂再花時間係間黑店到. 咁我唯有再dm個店主問佢想要貨既幾時送到, 佢一句&rsquo;等警方通知佢&rsquo;, 然後block哂所有post唔俾留言就算!<br />\n呢個店主真係夠理直氣壯, 完全覺得自己冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>雖然好少錢但助長呢啲仆街就係唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我唔知佢遲啲會唔會轉名, 大家見到記住小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\nSor for19999<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fd9g0yC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffd9g0yC.png&h=f1f87507&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWqHbFi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWqHbFi.png&h=0627e908&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBiBf6Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBiBf6Y.png&h=5efca555&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wohqTTE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwohqTTE.png&h=61ccc72c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGseNdF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGseNdF.png&h=628af804&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4y9AwFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4y9AwFk.png&h=0de2933e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5Udikm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5Udikm.png&h=b9eafdc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28dcd0d7a39f30df4d1c9343b5a054bf999047e0","tid":2329634,"uid":307180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"ig買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間舖仲要得200幾followers<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8018d2dc88501e20f8b3b1854715f08e13276dcb","tid":2329634,"uid":155815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"每星期都一單ig買野放上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連仔開返個賺物台啦屌<img src=\